Class LogicalResourceIterate

    • com.espertech.esper.eeutil.domain.push.LogicalResourceIterate

  • public class LogicalResourceIterate
extends java.lang.Object
    Defines update semantics, i.e. whether to observe+realtime listen, whether to iterate once on start or iterate only according to the pattern or both.
